<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>兼职投资人修炼手册 — 交互式看板</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --primary: #1a3a5c;
    --accent: #2d7dd2;
    --accent2: #e8a838;
    --green: #2ecc71;
    --red: #e74c3c;
    --bg: #f0f4f8;
    --card: #ffffff;
    --text: #1a2330;
    --text2: #5a6a7a;
    --border: #d8e4f0;
    --sidebar-w: 240px;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); display: flex; min-height: 100vh; }

  /* Sidebar */
  #sidebar {
    width: var(--sidebar-w); background: var(--primary); color: #fff;
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 100vh; overflow-y: auto;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; z-index: 100;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .sidebar-header { padding: 24px 16px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .sidebar-header h2 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; }
  .sidebar-header p { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top: 4px; }
  .nav-list { list-style: none; padding: 8px 0; flex: 1; }
  .nav-list li a {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; border-left: 3px solid transparent;
  }
  .nav-list li a:hover, .nav-list li a.active {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #fff; border-left-color: var(--accent2);
  }
  .nav-list li a .nav-icon { font-size: 16px; width: 20px; text-align: center; }
  .nav-badge {
    margin-left: auto; background: var(--accent2); color: #fff;
    font-size: 10px; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 10px;
  }

  /* Main content */
  #main { margin-left: var(--sidebar-w); flex: 1; padding: 0 0 60px; }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, #2d5a8e 100%);
    color: #fff; padding: 48px 40px 40px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '📈'; font-size: 200px; position: absolute; right: -20px; top: -30px;
    opacity: 0.06; line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero .tag { display: inline-block; background: var(--accent2); color: #fff; font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .hero p { font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .hero-meta { display: flex; gap: 24px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .hero-meta span { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }

  /* Section */
  section { padding: 32px 40px 0; }
  .section-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--text2); margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
  .section-title::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

  /* Cards grid */
  .cards-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 20px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .card-header { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .card-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 20px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .card-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3; }
  .card-sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text2); margin-top: 2px; }
  .card-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.6; }
  .card-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .tag-chip { font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text2); border: 1px solid var(--border); }

  /* Expandable card content */
  .card-expand { display: none; margin-top: 14px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .card-expand.open { display: block; }
  .card-expand ul { padding-left: 18px; }
  .card-expand ul li { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.8; }

  /* Path cards */
  .path-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
  .path-card { background: var(--card); border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid var(--border); padding: 20px; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .path-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .path-card.recommended { border-color: var(--accent2); }
  .path-card.recommended::before { content: '推荐'; position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 12px; background: var(--accent2); color: #fff; font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px; }
  .path-card { position: relative; }
  .path-num { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent); opacity: 0.3; }
  .path-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin: 4px 0 10px; }
  .path-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.6; }
  .path-fit { margin-top: 12px; font-size: 12px; padding: 8px 10px; background: var(--bg); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text2); }

  /* Table */
  .data-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; }
  .data-table th { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; }
  .data-table th:first-child { border-radius: 8px 0 0 0; }
  .data-table th:last-child { border-radius: 0 8px 0 0; }
  .data-table td { padding: 10px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .data-table tr:hover td { background: #f7fafc; }
  .data-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .table-wrap { background: var(--card); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); }

  /* Bias cards */
  .bias-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; }
  .bias-card { background: var(--card); border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 16px; border-left: 4px solid var(--red); }
  .bias-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .bias-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* Loss chart */
  .loss-bars { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .loss-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .loss-label { width: 80px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text2); text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .loss-bar-wrap { flex: 1; background: #fee; border-radius: 4px; height: 28px; position: relative; }
  .loss-bar { height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), #ff8080); border-radius: 4px; display: flex; align-items: center; padding-left: 8px; transition: width 1s ease; }
  .loss-bar span { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; white-space: nowrap; }
  .loss-need { width: 100px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--red); font-weight: 600; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; }
  .timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 12px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: var(--border); }
  .tl-item { position: relative; padding-bottom: 28px; }
  .tl-dot { position: absolute; left: -26px; top: 4px; width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); border: 3px solid #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent); }
  .tl-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .tl-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tl-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text2); line-height: 1.6; }
  .tl-actions { margin-top: 10px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .tl-action { font-size: 12px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text2); }

  /* Books */
  .books-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }
  .book-card {
    background: var(--card); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 16px; display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
    transition: all 0.2s; cursor: default;
  }
  .book-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .book-cover-wrap {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 72px; height: 100px;
    border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 2px 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    background: var(--bg);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .book-cover-wrap img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .book-cover-placeholder {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 28px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
    color: white;
  }
  .book-num { width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 5px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .book-meta { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .book-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .book-cat { font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .cat-intro { background: #e3f2fd; color: #1565c0; }
  .cat-philosophy { background: #fce4ec; color: #c62828; }
  .cat-stock { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32; }
  .cat-trade { background: #fff3e0; color: #e65100; }

  /* Progress checklist */
  .checklist { list-style: none; }
  .checklist li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .checklist li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .check-box {
    width: 20px; height: 20px; border: 2px solid var(--border); border-radius: 5px;
    flex-shrink: 0; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; margin-top: 1px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .check-box.checked { background: var(--green); border-color: var(--green); color: #fff; }
  .check-box.checked::after { content: '✓'; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; }
  .check-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--text); }
  .check-text.done { text-decoration: line-through; color: var(--text2); }

  /* Quote */
  .quote-block {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f7ff, #e8f4fd);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
    padding: 16px 20px; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic;
    color: var(--primary); line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .quote-block cite { display: block; margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; color: var(--text2); font-weight: 600; }

  /* Warning box */
  .warning-box {
    background: #fff8e1; border: 1px solid #ffcc02; border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 18px; font-size: 13px; color: #5d4037; line-height: 1.6;
    display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .warning-icon { font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  /* Formula box */
  .formula {
    background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 20px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.8; margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .formula strong { color: var(--accent2); }

  /* Stats row */
  .stats-row { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .stat-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px; flex: 1; min-width: 140px; }
  .stat-value { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); }
  .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text2); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* Scroll-to-top */
  #scrollTop {
    position: fixed; bottom: 24px; right: 24px; width: 44px; height: 44px;
    background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 18px; cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(45,125,210,0.4);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.2s;
    opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 200;
  }
  #scrollTop.visible { opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto; }
  #scrollTop:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); background: var(--primary); }

  /* Progress bar at top */
  #progress-bar { position: fixed; top: 0; left: var(--sidebar-w); right: 0; height: 3px; background: var(--accent2); transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left; z-index: 200; transition: transform 0.1s; }

  /* Color variants */
  .c1 { background: #e3f2fd; } .c1 .card-icon { background: #1565c0; }
  .c2 { background: #e8f5e9; } .c2 .card-icon { background: #2e7d32; }
  .c3 { background: #fff3e0; } .c3 .card-icon { background: #e65100; }
  .c4 { background: #fce4ec; } .c4 .card-icon { background: #c62828; }
  .c5 { background: #f3e5f5; } .c5 .card-icon { background: #6a1b9a; }
  .c6 { background: #e0f7fa; } .c6 .card-icon { background: #00695c; }
  .c7 { background: #f1f8e9; } .c7 .card-icon { background: #33691e; }
  .c8 { background: #fff8e1; } .c8 .card-icon { background: #f57f17; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    :root { --sidebar-w: 0px; }
    #sidebar { transform: translateX(-240px); }
    #sidebar.open { transform: translateX(0); --sidebar-w: 240px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 24px; }
    section { padding: 20px 20px 0; }
    .path-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero { padding: 32px 20px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="progress-bar"></div>

<!-- Sidebar -->
<nav id="sidebar">
  <div class="sidebar-header">
    <h2>兼职投资人(日股散户)<br>入门手册</h2>
    <p>2026年版 · 日本股市指南</p>
  </div>
  <ul class="nav-list">
    <li><a href="#hero" class="active"><span class="nav-icon">🏠</span>首页</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch0"><span class="nav-icon">📖</span>前言</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch1"><span class="nav-icon">💡</span>第一章 打破幻觉</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch2"><span class="nav-icon">🎯</span>第二章 定位与优势</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch3"><span class="nav-icon">🔱</span>第三章 投资哲学</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch4"><span class="nav-icon">🧠</span>第四章 心理建设</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch5"><span class="nav-icon">🧰</span>第五章 基础工具箱</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch6"><span class="nav-icon">🔍</span>第六章 选股方法</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch7"><span class="nav-icon">🛡️</span>第七章 风险管理</a></li>
    <li><a href="#ch8"><span class="nav-icon">🗺️</span>第八章 成长路线图</a></li>
    <li><a href="#appendix"><span class="nav-icon">📚</span>附录 书单</a></li>
    <li><a href="#checklist"><span class="nav-icon">✅</span>进度打卡</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- Main -->
<main id="main">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero" id="hero">
    <div class="tag">2026年版 · 综合框架</div>
    <h1>兼职投资人(日股散户)入门手册</h1>
    <p>基于12本经典投资书籍  ·  从入门到建立属于自己的投资体系</p>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span>📚 12本经典书籍</span>
      <span>📋 8个核心章节</span>
      <span>🗾 专注日本市场</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <section>
    <div class="stats-row" style="margin-top:8px;">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">7~10%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">全球股市历史年化回报率</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">&gt;80%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">主动基金10年内跑输指数</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">2~3x</div>
        <div class="stat-label">亏损的痛苦 远大于 盈利的快乐</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">5~8只</div>
        <div class="stat-label">初期投资组合推荐规模</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Preface -->
  <section id="ch0">
    <div class="section-title">📖 前言</div>
    <div class="card" style="max-width:100%;">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon" style="background:#1a3a5c; font-size:22px;">💬</div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-title">为什么需要这本手册？</div>
          <div class="card-sub">写给有正职工作、每周只有5~15小时投入研究的投资者</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        绝大多数投资书籍是为职业投资者或全职交易者写的，假设读者每天有大量时间盯盘。这本手册的目标，是帮助<strong>兼职投资人</strong>构建一套真正适合自己的投资体系。
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:14px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(200px,1fr)); gap:10px;">
        <div style="background:#f0f7ff;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;font-size:13px;"><strong>✅ 有稳定主业收入</strong><br><span style="color:var(--text2)">投资是副业</span></div>
        <div style="background:#f0f7ff;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;font-size:13px;"><strong>⏱ 时间有限</strong><br><span style="color:var(--text2)">每周5~15小时</span></div>
        <div style="background:#f0f7ff;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;font-size:13px;"><strong>🎯 长期积累财富</strong><br><span style="color:var(--text2)">非短期暴利</span></div>
        <div style="background:#f0f7ff;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;font-size:13px;"><strong>📖 愿意学习</strong><br><span style="color:var(--text2)">但不过度消耗精力</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Chapter 1 -->
  <section id="ch1">
    <div class="section-title">💡 第一章 · 打破三个幻觉</div>
    <div class="cards-grid">

      <div class="card c1" onclick="toggleExpand(this)">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-icon">💸</div>
          <div>
            <div class="card-title">幻觉一：股票是快速致富捷径</div>
            <div class="card-sub">来源：《漫步华尔街》《胆小鬼的亿万富翁入门》</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">80%的主动管理型基金在任意10年内跑输大盘指数。人类大脑偏好暴富故事，忽略同等数量的亏损案例。</div>
        <div class="card-expand">
          <div class="quote-block">
            股票市场不是财富的印钞机，它是财富的再分配机器。短期博弈中，一个人的收益必然对应另一个人的损失。
            <cite>— 整合自《漫步华尔街》</cite>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text2)"><strong>正确认知：</strong>全球股市历史年化回报约7~10%，扣除通胀后5~7%。通过复利积累，20~30年可让资产翻数倍。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tags"><span class="tag-chip">点击展开</span><span class="tag-chip">认知重建</span></div>
      </div>

      <div class="card c2" onclick="toggleExpand(this)">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-icon">👔</div>
          <div>
            <div class="card-title">幻觉二：分析师比个人更可靠</div>
            <div class="card-sub">来源：《败者的游戏》</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">机构投资者掌控80%以上市场交易量，公开信息几乎瞬间被定价。主动投资策略扣除费用后长期难以战胜指数基金。</div>
        <div class="card-expand">
          <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text2)"><strong>正确认知：</strong>不要盲目崇拜分析师，也不要完全忽视研报。学会用批判性思维阅读，关注分析师的推理过程，而非直接相信结论。</p>
        </div>
